title: Taylor Farms Florida Inc. Recalls Salads Containing Chicken Due To Misbranding and Undeclared Allergens
summary: WASHINGTON, May 26, 2016 Taylor Farms Florida, Inc., an Orlando, Fla. establishment, is recalling approximately 151 pounds of a chicken salad product due to misbranding and undeclared allergens, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today.
